<section xml:id="sec-fd-3-practice">
	<title>Deliberate Practice: Dividing Fractions</title>
    <p>
        Algebra is a skill, which means it requires practice to become proficient. But it will take more than rote
        repetition to get there. Deliberate practice is the thoughtful repetition of a task. For each of these sections,
        you will be given a list of specific skills or ideas to focus on as you practice thinking through the problems.
    </p>
	<p>
		<em>Focus on these skills:</em>
		<ul>
			<li>
				<p>
					Write the original expression. 
				</p>
			</li>
			<li>
				<p>
					Show the factoring and cancellation step. 
				</p>
			</li>
			<li>
				<p>
					Present your work legibly. 
				</p>
			</li>
		</ul>
	</p>
    <worksheet xml:id="sec-fd-3-worksheet">
		<p>
			<em>Instructions:</em> Perform the indicated calculation. 
		</p>
		<exercise>
			<p>
				Calculate <m>\displaystyle \frac{36}{35} \div \frac{21}{25}</m>. 
			</p>
		</exercise>
		<exercise>
			<p>
				Calculate <m>\displaystyle \frac{8}{15} \div \frac{20}{27}</m>. 
			</p>
		</exercise>
		<exercise>
			<p>
				Calculate <m>\displaystyle \frac{45}{28} \div \frac{15}{14}</m>. 
			</p>
		</exercise>
		<exercise>
			<p>
				Calculate <m>\displaystyle \frac{9x^2}{5y^3} \div \frac{6x y^2}{35}</m>. 
			</p>
		</exercise>
		<exercise>
			<p>
				Calculate <m>\displaystyle \frac{15b}{4a^2} \div \frac{9a^2 b^2}{10}</m>. 
			</p>
		</exercise>
		<exercise>
			<p>
				Calculate <m>\displaystyle \frac{9}{5n^2m^3} \div \frac{3 n m^2}{20}</m>. 
			</p>
		</exercise>
		<exercise>
			<p>
				Calculate <m>\displaystyle \frac{8xy^2}{15z^3} \div \frac{2yz^2}{21 x^4}</m>. 
			</p>
		</exercise>
		<exercise>
			<p>
				Calculate <m>\displaystyle \frac{14b^2}{3a^3 c^3} \div \frac{28a^2 b^3}{15c^3}</m>. 
			</p>
		</exercise>
		<exercise>
			<p>
				Calculate <m>\displaystyle \frac{2 x^2 (x + 3)}{3 (x - 4)^2} \div \frac{4(x + 3)}{15 x (x - 4)^2}</m>. 
			</p>
		</exercise>
		<exercise>
			<p>
				Calculate <m>\displaystyle \frac{15 (x - 3)^2 (x + 1)}{9(x + 3)^2} \div \frac{10 (x + 1)(x -3)}{3 (x + 3)^3}</m>. 
			</p>
		</exercise>
	</worksheet>
</section>
